        <hr>
        <ul class="pl-3">
            <li>
                <p> 
                    Your privacy is important to us. It is SetItUp's policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may
                    collect from you across our website, <a href="https://setitupcorp.herokuapp.com">https://setitupcorp.herokuapp.com</a>, and other sites we own and
